data.description: Price Adjustment - Beautiful ICI Home..3 bedrooms, one office and one flex room..Light and bright, open floor plan, like new, why wait to build? Flex room can be used as an office, den, study or, exercise room..Foyer leads into kitchen and dining area..Lots of room for large gatherings or relaxing..room leads into a screen, covered lanai plumbed for a summer kitchen..large, beautiful, fenced backyard with lots of privacy..large owners' suite with dual walk-in closets..interior laundry room, plumbed for water and sink, lots of storage, custom shelving/racks in garage..8 ft doors, high ceilings up to 14 ft..Tankless, hot water heater. Access to E Town's amenities that includes club facilities, community pool, fitness center, playground, dog park and walking and biking trail.
